## 1) Scroll-snap

```css
section {
    overflow-x: auto;
    overscroll-behavior-y: contain;
    scroll-snap-type: y mandatory;
}

section > picture{
    scroll-snap-align: center;
}
```

### List with Sub-List HTML

```html
<ul>
    <li><a herf="...">One</a></li>
    <li><a herf="..." aria-haspopup="true">TWO</a>
        <ul class=""dropdown" aria-label="submenu">
            <li><a herf="...">SUB-1</a></li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ul>
```
```css
li:hover > el,
li:focus > ul {
visibility: visible;
opacity: 1;

}
```

